# uptimerobot_maintenance_window (Data Source)

Looks up an existing UptimeRobot maintenance window without taking ownership of it. Use this when a maintenance window is managed outside the current Terraform state, but its ID is needed for monitor `maintenance_window_ids`.

The data source can look up a maintenance window by `id` or by exact `name`. Maintenance window names are not guaranteed unique; if more than one maintenance window has the same name, configure `id` to select one.

